    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently runs roughly and likely needs a major overhaul, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping during gear changes. Externally, there is substantial rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, and the paint has faded significantly over time. The interior shows heavy wear, including several tears in the upholstery and non-functioning electronic components like the radio and power windows. This car is best suited for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a project or as a source for spare parts.",
