    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my reliable ride, and she's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape, super clean inside, and totally ready for a new home! It runs like a dream and has plenty of life left for your daily commutes or weekend road trips. I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to help!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the robust 3.6L flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power across the rev range. The G96 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a chassis that benefits from factory-spec multi-link rear suspension and four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers. Maintained with technical rigor, the IMS bearing and rear main seal have been addressed, ensuring the M96 powerplant remains reliable. The exterior retains its aerodynamic profile with minor patina consistent with enthusiastic road use, while the interior remains a driver-focused cockpit. This is a mechanically sound example of Porsche\u2019s water-cooled evolution, balanced for both spirited canyon carving and high-speed stability.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Clean interior. Maintenance up to date.",
