      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through its 8,000 RPM redline. This example retains its crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with recent bushing refreshes and verified subframe integrity. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its driver-focused history, the VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. A purist\u2019s spec with high-revving throttle response and balanced weight distribution, ready for the technical driver.",
